description:
Background 
We are a SaaS team looking for a long term relationship with an excellent agency that has multiple developers and other resources.&nbsp;&nbsp;
This &ldquo;work to hire&rdquo; project will be an initial project to test if the developer is a good fit.&nbsp;&nbsp;
Upon successful completion of the initial project, the same developer will become part of our team to support and enhance our healthcare EMR system full time (40 hours per week in EST time zone).&nbsp;&nbsp;
Requirements 
1-Full Stack Senior Developer with at least 5 years experience
2-Experience in healthcare EMR and billing systems&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
3-Must work in the EST time zone until 5pm EST
4-Must have excellent communication skills including the ability to talk on the phone with team members and customers.&nbsp;&nbsp;You will attend a daily scrum meeting with at least one customer so you must have excellent English and be comfortable speaking.&nbsp;&nbsp;
5-Skills to enhance and troubleshoot existing platform written in C# ASP.NET MVC, jQuery, DevExpress, Entity Framework. Some pages have classic ASP which need upgrading.&nbsp;&nbsp;
6-Excellent DBA skills needed for Microsoft SQL Server to find and debug data issues
7-Work closely with the Vietnam development team.&nbsp;&nbsp;Overlap hours will need to be coordinated.
8-Developer must be part of an agency that has multiple developers and resources. 
Questions 
In your proposal, please answer the attached questions. <b>Skills</b>:        Microsoft SQL Server,                     Microsoft IIS,                     ASP.NET MVC,                     Web Development,                     Amazon Web Services
